divs: Sighting DetailsDuring the eclipse on May 5th 2012, my 10 year old daughter , began taking photos with her I phone. We had just left a communion party for a friend at a restaurant. We started heading home to Nj when she was taking the pictures. At the time, she didn't notice anything unusual. However, once we got home and were looking at the photos we were shocked to see that 3 other ufos were in the shots in addition to the eclipse.
